Unitron:



Unitron looked into a CR chamber, seeing Vulois.  He looked around, seeing no 
other bot.  Opening the CR chamber, he got a hold of the unconscious (is he?) 
Vulois and put him over his shoulder.

"This worthless labor is not my line of work..." he mumbled, heading off for 
Zardus' position.
